name: Fishtail Braid Bracelet
description:
Like a fishtail braid for your hair, but now on your wrist!

Bracelet is twice as long as a regular bracelet so that you are able to loop it around your wrist twice (see image). Goes great with any other bracelet or by itself. 

Rainbow colors are standard. If you would like to choose your own colors, please select the 'my own colors' pricing option. There is a $1 charge.
